>Since we've moved to beta13, I cannot do history searches using ESC-/?  Is
>there a mapping that I must perform manually even though I'm using "bindkey
>-v"?

We're now trying to be compatible with vi, rather than ksh.  / now does
*forward* history searches.  Use ? for backward searches.

